      "rationale": "Version control is in place but formal regression testing suite for the hemolysis power-law submodel has not been executed for the current solver release. Achieved level 1 is below the required level 2 for MRL 2; however, the assessment team judged the gap acceptable given the solver's commercial provenance."
    },
