      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests confirm solver convergence for rotating turbomachinery cases at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to rotating-frame Navier-Stokes; second-order convergence confirmed for velocity and pressure fields in representative pump geometry."
    },
