      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index (normalized index of hemolysis, NIH) compared to experimental measurements with quantified agreement metric.",
      "rationale": "NIH predictions agree with experimental data within ±15% across all 5 operating points; relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed for worst-case condition. Agreement metric satisfies MRL 2 threshold."
    },
