      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on the FDA generic pump geometry, which differs from the subject CPB device in impeller diameter and volute design. No validation has been performed on a geometry within the COU device family. The assessment team argued the FDA benchmark is the accepted community standard, but the geometric dissimilarity reduces relevance, placing achieved level at 1 against a required level of 2."
